				Tow Center for Digital Journalism, Columbia Journalism School, Nov. 27, 2012</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YdVCl4iD6CA">Keynote at Back To The Source, ACIJ Conference 2011, Robert Rosenthal youtube</a></li>
